    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Ready for Another Explosive Move in FNF]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.thetatrades.com/blog/2017/02/06/ready-for-another-explosive-move-in-fnf/"/>
    <updated>2017-02-06T20:36:32-08:00</updated>
